Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.39,0:00:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就一直很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 原來是千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇唬人家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又甩人啦 這個月已經是第幾個了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 別逗我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下 等一下我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個男生是男子游泳部的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他為什麼會跟你表白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...因為喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這問題你問他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 你這口吻 說得好像我一點魅力都沒有似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜對人家一無所知哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還認為表白會成功嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也有這個可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像把交往看得很隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想說「交往了就應該結婚」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴你太守舊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒說到這份上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你那明顯「隨便玩玩」的心態 我可不敢苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「隨便玩玩」...你會不會說得太過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 根據千鶴的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不先瞭解好對方 就不能表白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 凡事都有個順序
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相識 相知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在深刻瞭解對方之後 才最後表白心跡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點可是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算「光榮犧牲」也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是能傳達自己的心意給對方 那就很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種不是單純的自我滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不顧慮對方的思念 肯定是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因為老這麼說 才交不到男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樣樣都按著順序來 少女都變老太婆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜你自己到頭來不也是跟誰都沒好上過嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘛 又沒你那種堅信不疑的理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你想說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了第二學期 茜你就變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像變回剛進白稜那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 虧你還記得這麼清楚呢 都咸豐年間的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡過頭 然後遲到 學習也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣 只有自信比別人多一倍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘也忘不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現 現在我才不是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這份陽光氣息跟那時一樣 晶瑩通透啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 你是詩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 去美國留學那事進展得怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是英語什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這表情是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛入學的時候 英語不是糟透頂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點還是跟以前一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 餓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快淋個澡換身衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會先準備好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該在房間裡面學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 鳴海哥有沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒過來 貌似工作很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最近都沒怎麼來 有點點寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算「光榮犧牲」也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是能傳達自己的心意給對方 那就很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種不是單純的自我滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不顧慮對方的思念 肯定是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也沒來電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊 我想著等下去趟圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 最近都不能跟你一起學習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啦 茜自己也有很多事情要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留學的準備很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 鳴海哥都沒怎麼過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 之前不是天天都過來嗎 而且電話也...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之說他現在班制換了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才沒什麼時間過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 電話那方面...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上吃麵包？還是吃飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃麵包好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去泡紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝奶茶好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 下一句
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬱鬱相思苦 自甘絕此生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}玉の緒よ　絶えなば絶えね　ながらへば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苟延人世上 無計掩癡情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}忍ぶることの　弱りもぞする
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}(*這句摘自小倉百人一首 第89首)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念這一句的 是平安時代末期的和歌詩人兼王族式子內親王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 和風漢堡套餐以及炸蝦套餐 各一份對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲料要什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之很賣力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他之前太馬虎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個「時薪小偷」總算醒悟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長說根據孝之的表現 決定要給他加時薪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 真由真由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我親耳聽見的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 店長他在想什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他不懂什麼叫經營呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我深感抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身擔店長這個重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家添麻煩 我深感抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ha ha ha
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我總算也有了身為店長的自覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也開始形成有自己特色的一套經營理念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 真可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 真由真由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉雙手同意 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊毛出在羊身上 哪裡增加了再找個地方減掉就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方減掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道不這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由真由 貴客惠臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 要先下單再端水給他們才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順序反啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開 屎殼郎 別擋路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長 這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太寵她們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們啊 可是有陽光就燦爛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理 我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這個了 實在不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然拜託你改班制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡 鳴海你能多上幾個班 對我來說也是求之不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 我們情況樂觀多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海你這邊真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 你的私人時間不就沒有了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我想努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那我也沒有什麼要說的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 屎殼郎 你有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 挑這麼忙的時候來 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉啊 讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 我才是突然間跑到你工作的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是休息時間 給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准用敬語 我之前沒跟你說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:12:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ha ha ha 給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗓門還是跟以前一樣大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 我言行不謹慎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 知錯就去改吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 今天找我有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙她出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？這是我想問的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟姐姐之間發生什麼事了 鳴海哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在暫時保持一點距離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們之前不是還很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前還想 遙她現在很精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能待在她身邊 對她有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看來是我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事 姐姐她無論什麼時候都對鳴海哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙才沒有這麼軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她其實相當堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我這種人 要堅強的多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...就算是也不用...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己男友始終是個自由職業者 會讓遙很不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說「要配得起遙」這種說法很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但當我想了想今後的事 就覺得保持現狀可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙才沒有這麼軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她其實相當堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我這種人 要堅強得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「就如夜空中繁星般閃爍」...嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有真心喜歡過一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水月學姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 有什麼奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因 因為...那 就算鳴海哥選擇了姐姐 你也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他也會注視我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？我可沒說「你眼中只能有我一個」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說「希望你也能注視我」罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 你有真心喜歡過一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒試過的話 繼續說下去也不會有任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的話 也只是想法不同 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著這種話來逃避 我不能允許
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從最開始沒想過要你允許
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得鳴海哥很可憐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他哪裡可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還必須應酬你的鳴海哥的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你 絕對理解不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你 連存在本身都是失常的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我 也有真心喜歡的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼飛機啊 那是我要送的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼磨蹭誰有閒心等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼宮學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在擔心什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我今天想早點走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個 我叫做涼宮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 突然叫你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 為 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平學長你不是姐姐她們的摯友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摯友啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒聽過這個詞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟孝之談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽了他的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們 還是說「再見」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己決定的 「要跟遙一起活下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我能理解 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是為了遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了我的人生 才想這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最開始我的確很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他還是決定要尊重涼宮的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然孝之跟涼宮之間都發生了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總算能恢復原狀 不 總算能邁步向前了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我相信他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平學長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 抱歉 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 我馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 好痛啊 靠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才好像有人在看這邊...是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你丫 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「對不起 我不會重犯了」 來 說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂吠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少你也說日語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有反省的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 玉野
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9比1 我認為是前輩的壓倒性勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們幹活去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領著工資就得好好幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 給我去踩貓屎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 媽媽真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.38,0:22:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸今天可能會比較晚回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 媽媽 你做這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.56,0:23:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是習慣了連孝之那份也做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家努力吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天孝之不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝之也是要工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能勉強他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽我好寂寞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.24,0:23:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最近好像很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次記得轉告他有空隨時來家裡坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.46,0:23:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別騙我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？茜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你別再騙我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙是...指什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐說要跟鳴海哥分手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.15,0:23:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事 請你好好說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海哥他這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對他有什麼不滿 你倒是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 要吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.93,0:24:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是姐姐 你用得著這麼嬌慣她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽你也覺得奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.76,0:24:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海哥之前每天都過來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間就不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.36,0:24:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來每晚都會打個電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.67,0:24:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間也不打了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.18,0:24:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒察覺到才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.31,0:24:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜你不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.16,0:24:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.14,0:24:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我跟孝之的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟茜...沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.92,0:24:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係？你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.85,0:24:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧姐姐你還能這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.40,0:24:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海哥他幹活相當賣力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.96,0:24:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他相信姐姐 想跟姐姐你在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.77,0:24:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了跟姐姐的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.97,0:25:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他這麼努力 但不是很可憐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.34,0:25:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.01,0:25:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是姐姐你自己任性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.84,0:25:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要撒嬌撒到什麼地步才舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.66,0:25:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 你明明什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.55,0:25:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.97,0:25:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.74,0:25:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙！